text: Wu Bei (; born December 22, 1979) is a Chinese rhythmic gymnast. Wu competed for China in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. There she was 35th in the qualification round and didn't advance to the semifinal. == References == == External links == * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese rhythmic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of China
